column_glossary.Rd

Allowed column names in tidied tibbles

column_glossary

Format

A tibble with 4 variables:

method

One of "glance", "augment" or "tidy".

column

Character name of allowed output column.

description

Character description of expected column contents.

Examples

column_glossary
